ng%20a%20good%20drink%20but%20mentioned%20that%20it%20affects%20her%20more%2C%20requiring%20a%20few%20days%20of%20recovery%20afterward.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BRS%20or%20Congress%3A%20The%20Dilemma%20Facing%20Telangana%E2%80%99s%20Muslim%20Voters%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F06%2F02134601%2FUntitled-design-2022-06-02T134549.709.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20August%20this%20year%2C%20Telangana%20chief%20minister%20K.%20Chandrashekhar%20Rao%20(KCR)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fhyderabad%2Ftelangana-kcr-temple-church-mosque-secretariat-8829385%2F%5C%22%3Einaugurated%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20the%20sprawling%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20Secretariat%20complex%2C%20a%20tastefully%20designed%20mosque.%20For%20many%2C%20this%20move%20marked%20the%20possible%20dousing%20of%20a%20controversy%20in%20an%20election%20year.%20For%2C%20it%20was%20in%202020%20that%20the%20Telangana%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.siasat.com%2Fhyderabad-2-mosques-temple-demolished-for-new-secretariat-1920607%2F%5C%22%3Erazed%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20along%20with%20the%20old%20secretariat%20buildings%2C%20two%20mosques%20(and%20a%20temple)%20that%20existed%20within%20the%20complex.%20While%20there%20were%20murmurs%20of%20a%20possible%20demolition%20of%20the%20old%20secretariat%2C%20the%20flattening%20of%20the%20mosques%20was%20unexpected.%20This%20sent%20shockwaves%20within%20the%20Muslim%20community%20and%20thus%20followed%20sporadic%20low-key%20demonstrations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20reconstruction%20of%20these%20mosques%2C%20given%20that%20the%20state%20goes%20to%20the%20polls%2C%20appears%20an%20attempt%20to%20mollify%20the%20Muslim%20community%20%E2%80%93%20which%20constitutes%2012.68%25%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20population%20of%203.51%20crore.%20At%20the%20event%2C%20Rao%20was%20flanked%20by%20Hyderabad%20MP%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%2C%20and%20the%20Muslim%20clergy%2C%20including%20Mufti%20Khaleel%20Ahmed%20who%20heads%20the%20Jamia%20Nizamia%2C%20an%20influential%20seminary%20founded%20in%201872.%20Muftis%20(qualified%20clerics)%20at%20the%20Jamia%E2%80%99s%20Darul%20Ifta%20(Fatwa%20Centre)%20have%20been%20issuing%20fatwas%20(jurisprudential%20opinions)%2C%20which%20is%20why%20the%20mufti%E2%80%99s%20presence%20was%20significant%20at%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CNot%20one%2C%20but%20I%20saw%20four%20muftis%20there%20(at%20the%20inauguration).%20When%20muftis%20prayed%20there%2C%20the%20question%20(of%20validity%20of%20prayers)%20does%20not%20arise%2C%E2%80%9D%20Owaisi%20told%20the%20media%2C%20hours%20after%20the%20inauguration%2C%20giving%20validity%20to%20the%20event%20by%20invoking%20Mufti%20Khaleel%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cservice%20of%20six%20decades%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20faith.%20Owaisi%20also%20compared%20KCR%E2%80%99s%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS)%20government%20with%20that%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20and%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20former%20had%20reconstructed%20the%20mosque%20after%20demolishing%20it%2C%20a%20promise%20that%20the%20Congress%20failed%20to%20keep%20after%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20was%20razed.%20It%20is%20a%20comparison%20he%20continues%20to%20reiterate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F30185604%2FFij69mfVIAMVzO0.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F30185604%2FFij69mfVIAMVzO0.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F30185604%2FFij69mfVIAMVzO0-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F30185604%2FFij69mfVIAMVzO0-1024x683.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-630861%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAIMIM%20president%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40asadowaisi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EEven%20as%20the%20elections%2C%20slated%20for%20November%2030%2C%20inch%20closer%2C%20Owaisi%20and%20his%20younger%20brother%20Akbaruddin%20Owaisi%20have%20been%20launching%20salvos%2C%20primarily%20against%20the%20Congress%2C%20all%20the%20while%20defending%20KCR.%20This%20is%20symptomatic%20of%20the%20dilemma%20a%20section%20of%20the%20Muslim%20community%20finds%20itself%20in%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20to%20support%20the%20BRS%20for%20a%20third%20term%2C%20despite%20having%20certain%20reservations%2C%20or%20voting%20to%20bring%20the%20Congress%20back%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20meetings%20and%20consultations%20about%20what%20the%20BRS%20government%20did%2C%20and%20didn%E2%80%99t%20do%20for%20the%20Muslims.%20A%20document%20called%20%E2%80%98Muslim%20Declaration%202023%E2%80%99%20was%20released%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Hyderabad-based%20social%20activist%20Khalida%20Parveen.%20Figuring%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20list%20was%20the%20BRS%E2%80%99s%20unkept%20promise%20of%2012%25%20reservations%20for%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIt%20was%20in%202014%20that%20the%20BRS%20%5Bthen%20TRS%5D%20supremo%2C%20near%20Shadnagar%2C%20a%20town%20about%2040%20km%20from%20Hyderabad%2C%20had%20pledged%20to%20accord%2012%25%20reservations%20for%20Muslims.%20This%20unkept%20promise%20has%20remained%20a%20key%20talking%20point%20with%20those%20who%20question%20the%20BRS.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20our%20meetings%2C%20we%20saw%20Muslims%20from%20across%20the%20state%20were%20unhappy%20with%20KCR.%20Of%20course%2C%20the%2012%25%20reservation%20promise%20was%20not%20kept.%20Other%20issues%20like%20low%20representation%20of%20Muslims%20in%20the%20assembly%20are%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20claimed%20Parveen.%20While%20the%20state%20has%20119%20assembly%20constituencies%2C%20the%20BRS%E2%80%99s%20candidates%20list%20has%20only%20three%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EInterestingly%2C%20it%20was%20the%20BRS%20government%20that%20constituted%20a%20Commission%20of%20Inquiry%20to%20study%20the%20socio-economic%20conditions%20of%20the%20Muslim%20community.%20Comprising%20development%20economist%20Amir%20Ullah%20Khan%2C%20academician%20Abdul%20Shaban%2C%20and%20headed%20by%20former%20civil%20servant%20G.%20Sudhir%2C%20the%20commission%E2%80%99s%20report%20%E2%80%93%20which%20was%20released%20in%202016%20%E2%80%93%20made%20a%20case%20for%20reservations%20to%20Muslims.%20But%20before%20making%20this%20recommendation%2C%20the%20Commission%20noted%20that%20in%20the%20Telangana%20government%E2%80%99s%2023%20departments%2C%20the%20share%20of%20Muslim%20employees%20was%20about%207.36%25.%20This%20was%20not%20in%20proportion%20to%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20Muslim%20population%20of%2012.36%25.%20It%20also%20underscored%20the%20low%20representation%20of%20Muslims%20in%20the%20bureaucracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMaking%20a%20case%20for%20reservations%2C%20the%20Commission%20stated%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20also%20been%20found%20that%20under%E2%80%93representation%20of%20Muslims%20is%20acute%20in%20departments%20where%20there%20are%20large%20numbers%20of%20employees%2C%20or%20the%20departments%20which%20are%20strategic%20in%20nature.%20For%20instance%2C%20administrative%20service%2C%20Home%2C%20Education%20and%20Welfare%20Departments.%20These%20four%20sectors%2Fdepartments%20are%20crucial%20for%20include%20development%20and%20have%20relatively%20high%20under-representation%20of%20Muslims.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ESome%20activists%20and%20the%20public%20in%20general%20on%20several%20occasions%20have%20expressed%20their%20displeasure%2C%20and%20cite%20this%20as%20an%20example%20of%20how%20the%20BRS%20has%20taken%20the%20Muslim%20community%20for%20granted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EClarifying%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20position%20during%20an%20assembly%20session%2C%20CM%20KCR%20reiterated%20that%20the%20assembly%20had%20passed%20a%20resolution%20in%20the%20house%20for%20the%20reservations.%20It%20was%20the%20Union%20government%20that%20kept%20it%20pending.%20Another%20resolution%20was%20also%20passed%20and%20sent%2C%20in%20case%20the%20Union%20government%20keeps%20the%20issue%20hanging%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ES.Q.%20Masood%2C%20an%20activist%20who%20was%20not%20a%20part%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Muslim%20Declaration%202023%E2%80%99%2C%20said%20that%20the%20BRS%20was%20%E2%80%9Cdangling%20a%20carrot%E2%80%9D%20in%20front%20of%20the%20community.%20%E2%80%9CIn%202019%2C%20KCR%20spoke%20about%20redoing%20the%20resolution%20exercise.%20Does%20this%20mean%20the%20BRS%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20solid%20legal%20strategy%3F%20But%2C%20the%2012%25%20reservation%20is%20one%20of%20many%20issues.%20A%20win%20for%20the%20KCR%20government%20is%20that%20they%20have%20kept%20law%20and%20order%20in%20check%2C%20and%20no%20major%20communal%20issue%20has%20taken%20place%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20upholding%20of%20communal%20amity%2C%20and%20keeping%20a%20check%20on%20possibilities%20of%20communal%20conflagration%2C%20according%20to%20many%2C%20is%20crucial%20and%20works%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20BRS%20government.%20The%20fact%20that%20T.%20Raja%20Singh%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fraja-singh-goshamahal-hyderabad-hindutva-profile%5C%22%3Econtroversial%20BJP%20legislator%3C%2Fa%3E%20currently%20under%20suspension%2C%20was%20arrested%20under%20the%20Preventive%20Detention%20Act%20for%20his%20derogatory%20comments%20about%20Prophet%20Muhammad%20is%20a%20case%20in%20point.%20The%20move%20was%20lauded%20as%20the%20BRS%E2%80%99s%20policy%20of%20zero%20tolerance%20for%20communalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22hi%5C%22%3E%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%AC%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%A7%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%AE%2C%20%E0%A4%AD%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%BE%2C%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%82%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%83%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%BF%2C%20%E0%A4%96%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A8-%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A8%20%E0%A4%85%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%97-%E0%A4%85%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%97%20%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%8B%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%A4%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%88%E0%A5%A4%20%E0%A4%B2%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%A8%20%E0%A4%A4%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%82%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%AF%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%AD%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%8F%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%9C%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%9F%20%E0%A4%94%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%AC%E0%A5%82%E0%A4%A4%20%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%96%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%88%20%E0%A4%A6%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%A4%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%88%E0%A4%82%E0%A5%A4%20%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%B9%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%96%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%AF%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%82%E0%A4%A4%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%9A%E0%A4%82%E0%A4%A6%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%B6%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%96%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B5%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%A4%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%85%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%88%2C%20%E0%A4%9C%E0%A5%8B%20%E0%A4%85%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%8F%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%8B%20%E0%A4%AA%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%A4%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%A4%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%88%E0%A5%A4%20%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%B9%E