trong%3EFragmentation%20may%20benefit%20BJP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWhat%20worries%20a%20section%20of%20Muslims%20is%20the%20fragmentation%20of%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20vote.%20This%20vote%2C%20split%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BRS%2C%20could%20potentially%20be%20devastating.%20An%20office%20bearer%20of%20an%20influential%20socio-religious%20organisation%20who%20did%20not%20wish%20to%20be%20identified%20said%20that%20while%20the%20Congress%20may%20be%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Cslightly%20better%E2%80%9D%20position%20in%20Telangana%20given%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20win%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20a%20feeling%20of%20anti-incumbency%20against%20the%20BRS%2C%20there%20was%20no%20Congress%20wave.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Congress%20in%20Telangana%20is%20an%20unproven%20entity%2C%20and%20appears%20weak%20at%20the%20grassroots%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9COn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20BRS%20may%20be%20facing%20anti-incumbency%2C%20but%20the%20party%20is%20strong%20at%20the%20grassroots.%20If%20the%20Muslim%20vote%20is%20divided%20between%20the%20BRS%20and%20Congress%2C%20it%20would%20lead%20to%20problems%20in%20constituencies%20in%20the%20composite%20Nizamabad%2C%20and%20Adilabad%20districts%2C%20where%20their%20vote%20is%20important%2C%20and%20benefit%20the%20BJP.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWhile%20there%20may%20be%20an%20impression%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20weakened%2C%20this%20is%20likely%20not%20the%20case%2C%20the%20analyst%20said.%20The%20BJP%20vote%20bank%20will%20continue%20to%20hold%20its%20own.%20%E2%80%9CG.%20Kishan%20Reddy%20is%20the%20new%20BJP%20president%2C%20but%20(former%20BJP%20president)%20Bandi%20Sanjay%20continues%20to%20enjoy%20popularity%2C%20especially%20among%20the%20youth.%20The%20party%20is%20likely%20to%20add%20a%20few%20more%20seats%20in%20the%20upcoming%20elections%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EProfessor%20Afroz%20Alam%2C%20who%20heads%20the%20Department%20of%20Political%20Science%20at%20the%20Maulana%20Azad%20National%20Urdu%20University%20and%20has%20been%20studying%20the%20election%20climate%20with%20his%20team%2C%20said%20that%20the%20Congress%20versus%20BRS%20narrative%20in%20Telangana%20is%20largely%20class-based.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20clear%20divide.%20Elite%20Muslims%20are%20tilting%20towards%20the%20Congress.%20Among%20rural%20Muslims%20who%20are%20beneficiaries%20of%20government%20schemes%2C%20there%20is%20a%20preference%20for%20KCR%2C%E2%80%9D%20Alam%20said.%20He%20opined%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20and%20the%20recent%20win%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20Karnataka%20have%20had%20a%20bearing%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9Celites%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%20opinion.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20little%20or%20no%20anti-incumbency%20against%20BRS%2C%20but%20there%20is%20discontent%20with%20some%20MLAs.%20In%20Karnataka%2C%20everybody%20wanted%20to%20defeat%20the%20BJP.%20In%20Telangana%2C%20that%20situation%20does%20not%20apply%2C%E2%80%9D%20Alam%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697700620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F06%2F02134601%2FUntitled-design-2022-06-02T134549.709.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-muslim-voters-dilemma-congress-brs%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20chief%20minister%20K.%20Chandrashekhar%20Rao%20is%20appreciated%20for%20maintaining%20communal%20amity%2C%20there%20is%20also%20some%20disappointment%20that%20his%20government%20could%20not%20deliver%20on%20the%20promise%20of%20reservations%20for%20the%20minority%20community.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-muslim-voters-dilemma-congress-brs%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A