20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Ffugitive-financier-jho-low-denies-being-mastermind-behind-1mdb-2020-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJho%20Low%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Malaysian%20financier%20accused%20of%20playing%20a%20central%20role%20in%20a%20massive%20%244.5%20billion%20fraud%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDavid%20Kenner%2C%20an%20attorney%20known%20for%20representing%20Suge%20Knight%2C%20Tupac%20Shakur%2C%20and%20Snoop%20Dogg%2C%20ran%20Michel's%20defense%20for%20the%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Michel's%20new%20lawyers%2C%20a%20legal%20team%20from%20ArentFox%20Schiff%2C%20now%20say%20Kenner%20botched%20the%20defense%20by%20using%20an%20%26quot%3Bexperimental%20artificial%20intelligence%20program%26quot%3B%20to%20draft%20his%20closing%20arguments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20Monday%20filing%20seen%20by%20Insider%2C%20Michel's%20lawyers%20alleged%20that%20Kenner%20used%20a%20program%20called%20EyeLevel.AI%2C%20and%20was%20%26quot%3Bignoring%20the%20best%20arguments%20and%20conflating%20the%20charged%20schemes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMichel%20never%20had%20a%20chance%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ArentFox%20Schiff%20team%20wrote%2C%20adding%20that%20Michel's%20legal%20defense%20was%20%26quot%3Bdeficient%20throughout.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichel's%20lawyers%20said%20his%20former%20publicist%20told%20them%20about%20Kenner%20using%20EyeLevel.AI%20to%20write%20the%20closing%20arguments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20pointed%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eyelevel.ai%2Fpost%2Ffirst-use-of-ai-in-federal-trial%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMay%2010%20product%20update%20%3C%2Fa%3Eby%20EyeLevel.AI%2C%20which%20said%20that%20Kenner%20had%20used%20the%20program%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bfirst%20use%20of%20generative%20AI%20in%20a%20federal%20trial.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20an%20absolute%20game%20changer%20for%20complex%20litigation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20press%20release%20cited%20Kenner%20as%20saying.%20%26quot%3BThe%20system%20turned%20hours%20or%20days%20of%20legal%20work%20into%20seconds.%20This%20is%20a%20look%20into%20the%20future%20of%20how%20cases%20will%20be%20conducted.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEyeLevel.AI%20said%20its%20system%20%26quot%3Bhelps%20lawyers%20become%2010x%20faster%20and%20more%20effective.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichel's%20lawyers%20also%20accused%20Kenner%20and%20his%20co-counsel%20of%20holding%20an%20undisclosed%20financial%20stake%20in%20EyeLevel.AI%2C%20and%20alleged%20that%20the%20pair%20used%20the%20program%20for%20Michel's%20defense%20so%20they%20could%20issue%20the%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ArentFox%20Schiff%20team%20alleged%20that%20law%20firms%20for%20Kenner%20and%20his%20co-counsel%20share%20addresses%20with%20CaseFile%20Connect%20%E2%80%94%20a%20technology%20partner%20with%20EyeLevel.AI.%20These%20firms%20are%20located%20in%20Encino%2C%20California%2C%20and%20New%20York%20City%2C%20per%20ArentFox%20Schiff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyers%20said%20this%20%26quot%3Bappears%20to%20confirm%26quot%3B%20that%20Kenner%20had%20a%20financial%20interest%20in%20the%20AI%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEyeLevel.AI%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Insider%20sent%20outside%20regular%20business%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20told%20several%20outlets%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20Kenner%20and%20his%20co-counsel%20don't%20have%20any%20stake%20in%20EyeLevel.AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNeither%20Kenner%20Law%20nor%20its%20associates%20have%20a%20financial%20stake%20in%20EyeLevel%20as%20claimed%20in%20the%20filing.%20They%20were%20happy%20with%20our%20AI's%20capabilities%20and%20provided%20a%20quote%20for%20a%20press%20release%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thedailybeast.com%2Fdavid-kenner-star-hip-hop-lawyer-accused-of-using-ai-in-big-case-he-lost%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEyeLevel.AI%20told%20The%20Daily%20Beast.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Aren