ournalist%20Soumya%20Vishwanathan.%20A%20news%20producer%20with%20Headlines%20Today%2C%20she%20had%20stayed%20back%20late%20to%20help%20out%20with%20a%20breaking%20news%20event.%20Her%20work%20done%2C%20she%20left%20the%20Jhandewalan%20office%20at%203.03%20am%2C%20got%20into%20her%20car%20and%20drove%20home%20to%20Vasant%20Kunj.%20She%20didn't%20know%20this%20drive%20would%20be%20her%20last%2C%20that%20a%20late-night%20robbery%20attempt%20would%20brutally%20cut%20her%20life%20short.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20Delhi%20court%20yesterday%20convicted%20five%20men%20in%20the%2015-year-old%20murder%20case.%20Four%20accused%20-%20Ravi%20Kapoor%2C%20Amit%20Shukla%2C%20Baljit%20Malik%20and%20Akshay%20Kumar%20--%20were%20held%20guilty%20of%20murder%20and%20loot.%20The%20fifth%2C%20Ajay%20Sethi%2C%20was%20held%20guilty%20of%20helping%20the%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20her%20way%20back%2C%20Soumya%20overtook%20a%20car%20occupied%20by%20Kapoor%2C%20Shukla%2C%20Kumar%20and%20Malik%2C%20police%20officers%20who%20probed%20the%20case%20have%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20four%20convicts%2C%20police%20said%2C%20noticed%20that%20the%20woman%20driver%20who%20overtook%20them%20was%20alone.%20They%20sped%20up%20and%20started%20following.%20First%2C%20they%20tried%20to%20intercept%20Soumya's%20car.%20She%20did%20not%20stop.%20Kapoor%20then%20fired%20at%20her%20with%20a%20countrymade%20weapon.%20The%20bullet%20hit%20her%20on%20the%20head%2C%20killing%20her%20instantly.%20The%20car%20crashed%20against%20a%20divider%20on%20Nelson%20Mandela%20Marg%2C%20close%20to%20her%20home%2C%20and%20came%20to%20a%20halt.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20killers%20fled%20the%20scene%2C%20an%20officer%20said%2C%20but%20returned%2020%20minutes%20later%20to%20check%20the%20victim's%20condition.%20When%20they%20saw%20police%20personnel%2C%20they%20ran%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAround%203.45%20am%2C%20a%20staff%20of%20a%20nearby%20restaurant%20cycling%20home%20saw%20a%20woman%20in%20the%20car%2C%20with%20its%20headlights%20and%20engine%20on.%20He%20stopped%20a%20couple%20of%20vehicles%20and%20then%20called%20the%20cops.%20Soumya%20was%20rushed%20to%20AIIMS%20where%20she%20was%20declared%20dead.%20During%20their%20investigation%2C%20police%20found%20that%20Soumya%20had%20called%20her%20father%20around%203.15%20am%20and%20told%20him%20that%20she%20was%20on%20her%20way.%20In%20less%20than%20half%20an%20hour%2C%20she%20was%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPolice%20later%20found%20her%20phone%20and%20wallet%20in%20the%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20investigation%20in%20the%20case%20was%20conducted%20by%20police%20from%20Delhi%20South%20district%2C%20then%20under%20HGS%20Dhaliwal%2C%20now%20special%20commissioner%20of%20Delhi%20Police%20special%20cell.%20Speaking%20to%20the%20media%20after%20the%20verdict%20yesterday%2C%20the%20senior%20officer%20said%20it%20was%20a%20challenging%20case%20as%20there%20was%20no%20physical%20contact%20between%20the%20victim%20and%20the%20killers.%20%26quot%3BOnly%20a%20bullet%20was%20fired%20from%20a%20moving%20vehicle%20that%20hit%20Soumya%2C%20killing%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20The%20officer%20said%20the%20family%20had%20also%20been%20offered%20a%20CBI%20investigation%2C%20but%20they%20decided%20to%20stick%20with%20Delhi%20Police.%20He%20said%20he%20is%20happy%20that%20Delhi%20Police%20lived%20up%20to%20the%20faith.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPolice%20made%20a%20breakthrough%20in%20the%20Soumya%20Vishwanathan%20murder%20case%20during%20its%20probe%20into%20the%20murder%20of%20another%20woman%2C%20Jigisha%20Ghosh%2C%20in%202009.%20Ghosh%20was%20looted%20and%20murdered%20on%20March%2018%2C%202009.%20Ravi%20Kapoor%20was%20arrested%20in%20this%20connection.%20And%20during%20questioning%2C%20he%20said%20they%20had%20murdered%20another%20woman.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYesterday's%20ruling%20brings%20some%20closure%20to%20Soumya's%20loved%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20Today%20News%20Director%20Rahul%20Kanwal%2C%20who%20was%20Soumya's%20colleague%20at%20the%20time%2C%20was%20at%20the%20court%20for%20the%20verdict.%20%26quot%3BSoumya%20Vishwanathan%20was%20the%20brightest%20young%20producer%20I%20have%20had%20the%20privilege%20of%20working%20with.%20On%20the%20night%20she%20was%20murdered%2C%20Soumya%20had%20stayed%20back%20after%20finishing%20the%20afternoon%20shift%20to%20help%20the%20night%20team%20prepare%20for%20the%20morning%20show.%20There%20had%20been%20a%20major%20terror%20attack%20and%20the%20newsroom%20was%20stretched%20covering%20the%20breaking%20news.%20Soumya%20was%20the%20flag-bearer%20of%20commitment%20and%20hard%20work%20in%20our%20newsroom%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHer%20gruesome%20murder%20on%20the%20way%20back%20home%20has%20haunted%20me%20for%2015%20years.%20Was%20filled%20with%20emotion%20and%20relief%20as%20I%20heard%20Judge%20Pandey%20pronounce%20all%20the%20accused%20guilty%20in%20a%20crowded%20Saket%20courtroom%20this%20afternoon.%20Nothing%20will%20bring%20Soumya%20back%20but%20at%20least%20the%20murderers%20will%20pay%20for%20their%20crime%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20verdict%2C%20Soumya's%20parents%20Madhavi%20Vishwanathan%20and%20MK%20Vishwanathan%20fought%20back%20tears.%20Speaking%20to%20the%20media%2C%20Ms%20Vishwanathan%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20lost%20our%20daughter%2C%20but%20this%20will%20act%20as%20a%20deterrent%20for%20others%20otherwise%20they%20(the%20convicts)%20would%20have%20been%20emboldened.%20At%20least%2C%20one%20gang%20would%20be%20out.%20That's%20all.%26quot%3B%20She%20said%20she%20wants%20life%20sentence%20for%20the%20convicts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697692560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2Fvlxuj687da_soumya-viswanathan_625x300.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsoumya-viswanathan-murder-case-delhi-police-soumya-vishwanathan-called-father-after-leaving-work-didnt-make-it-home-4494748%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22