%3E.%20The%20bullet%20hit%20her%20in%20the%20temple%20leaving%20her%20dead%20on%20the%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVishwanathan's%20car%20stopped%20after%20ramming%20into%20a%20divider.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20the%20accused%20fled%20from%20the%20spot%20but%2020%20minutes%20later%20returned%20to%20see%20her%20condition.%20When%20they%20saw%20police%20personnel%2C%20they%20ran%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20very%20satisfied%20today.%20The%20conviction%20has%20happened%20basically%20due%20to%20three%20reasons%20-%20weapon%20of%20offence%20which%20was%20recovered%20from%20the%20accused%2C%20the%20forensic%20sketch%20of%20the%20spot%2C%20and%20the%20sequence%20of%20incident%20matched%20with%20the%20confession%20statement%20of%20the%20accused%2C%26quot%3B%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697691420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F8v692fm_soumya-vishwanathan_625x300_19_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fsoumya-vishwanathan-journalist-murder-case-how-a-tattoo-wireless-set-led-cops-to-soumya-vishwanathans-killers-4494560%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20hand%20tattoo%2C%20a%20wireless%20set%20stolen%20from%20a%20policeman%2C%20and%20CCTV%20footage%20helped%20Delhi%20Police%20crack%20the%20case%20of%20the%20killing%20of%20IT%20professional%20Jigisha%20Ghosh%20and%20eventually%20led%20the%20investigators%20to%20the%20killers%20of%20TV%20journalist%20Soumya%20Vishwanathan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fsoumya-vishwanathan-journalist-murder-case-how-a-tattoo-wireless-set-led-cops-to-soumya-vishwanathans-killers-4494560%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww