shok%20Tandon.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20chapter%20(in%20the%20book)%20is%20on%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20-%20an%20apostle%20of%20peace%20for%20Britons.%20We%20are%20all%20disciples%20of%20the%20Father%20of%20the%20Nation.%20His%20role%20in%20building%20India%2C%20creating%20a%20link%20between%20an%20elitist%20national%20movement%20and%20the%20masses%2C%20fusing%20that%2C%20(all%20that)%20is%20very%20well%20documented%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Puri%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EWith%20several%20friends%20from%20my%20college%20days%20%26amp%3B%20former%20colleagues%20as%20part%20of%20the%20distinguished%20audience%2C%20launch%20of%20the%20book%20%E2%80%98The%20Reverse%20Swing%3A%20Colonialism%20to%20Cooperation'%20by%20another%20good%20friend%20for%20the%20past%20many%20decades%2C%20Sh%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAshokTandon%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40AshokTandon%3C%2Fa%3E%20Ji%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20reunion%20of%20sorts!%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FwtxXMNVEoA%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FwtxXMNVEoA%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Puri%20(%40HardeepSPuri)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHardeepSPuri%2Fstatus%2F1714637175097368680%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2018%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20let%20me%20tell%20you%20Mahatma%20himself%20was%20quite%20a%20complicated%20being%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BWhile%20still%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20he%20(Gandhi)%20actually%20asked%20for%20mobilisation%20of%20India's%20help%20for%20the%20war%20effort%20in%20the%20First%20World%20War.%20That's%20well%20documented.%26quot%3B%20Puri%20said%20that%20Gandhi's%20%26quot%3Binitial%20life%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20and%20his%20education%20prepared%20him%20for%20an%20%26quot%3BEnglish-style%20barrister%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20he%20goes%20to%20South%20Africa%2C%20it%20is%20then%20the%20Gandhi%20that%20we%20know%20and%20the%20Gandhi%20who%20contributed%20to%20our%20national%20movement%20begins%20to%20mature%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20content%20of%20the%20book%2C%20Mr%20Puri%20said%20there%20is%20a%20chapter%20in%20it%20about%20how%20India%20overtook%20the%20UK%20to%20become%20the%20world's%20fifth-largest%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20most%20of%20us%20relish%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20become%20the%20third%20largest%20economy%20and%20we%20overtake%20Japan%20and%20Germany%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20we%20will%20enjoy%20that%20much.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20minister%20said%20the%20Indo-British%20cooperation%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Baviation%20sector%2C%20telecommunications%2C%20all%20these%26quot%3B%20are%20relevant%20in%20understanding%20the%20dynamics%20of%20the%20current%20bilateral%20relationship%20between%20India%20and%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian-origin%20community%20in%20the%20UK%20has%20given%20%26quot%3Bshape%20and%20content%26quot%3B%20to%20India's%20relationship%20with%20the%20UK%20far%20more%20than%20what%20a%20diaspora%20can%20do%20elsewhere%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20hope%20the%20India-UK%20free%20trade%20agreement%20actually%20sees%20the%20light%20of%20the%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EParticipating%20in%20a%20panel%20discussion%20on%20the%20book%2C%20Tondon%2C%20the%20author%2C%20talked%20about%20a%20chapter%20on%20the%20Jallianwala%20Bagh%20Massacre%20and%20said%20many%2C%20from%20the%20Queen%20to%20the%20British%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20have%20expressed%20regret%20over%20the%20incident%20but%20they%20have%20never%20officially%20apologised%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIs%20it%20something%20to%20do%20with%20the%20British%20system%20that%20when%20you%20apologised%20for%20some%20crime%20and%20there%20is%20a%20provision%20for%20(giving)%20compensation%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697686260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fv93afb2g_hardeep-singh-puri-twitter-_625x300_19_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funion-minister-hardeep-singh-puri-mahatma-gandhi-was-quite-a-complicated-being-4494594%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20role%20and%20contribution%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20in%20India's%20freedom%20struggle%20is%20well%20documented%20and%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bquite%20a%20complicated%20being%26quot%3B%2C%20Union%20Minister%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Puri%20said%20on%20Wednesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funion-minister-hardeep-singh-puri-mahatma-gandhi-was-quite-a-complicated-being-4494594%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funion-minister-hardeep-singh-puri-mahatma-gandhi-was-quite-a-complicated-being-4494594%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funion-minister-hardeep-singh-puri-mahatma-gandhi-was-quite-a-complicated-being-4494594%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Telangana%20Polls%3A%20BRS%20Has%20Reason%20Not%20To%20Be%20Overconfident%20With%20Congress%20Poised%20To%20Challenge%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18190018%2Fcollage-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EHyderabad%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Five%20years%20can%20be%20a%20long%20time%2C%20especially%20in%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20thumping%20victory%20in%20the%20assembly%20elections%20in%20late%202018%2C%20the%20Bh