ductive%20answers%20to%20questions%20asked%20of%20them%20by%20the%20government%20and%20the%20defense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%2018%20people%20devoting%20time%20here%20to%20this%20case%2C%20and%20it's%20really%20a%20crime%2C%20that%20part%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Kaplan%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20jury%2C%20which%20was%20not%20in%20the%20room%20at%20the%20time.%20%26quot%3BObviously%2C%20it's%20a%20serious%20case.%20Obviously%2C%20there%20are%20all%20kinds%20of%20important%20things%20to%20be%20determined.%20But%20lawyers%20are%20supposed%20to%20do%20a%20little%20better%20than%20this.%20I%20am%20talking%20to%20both%20sides.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EProsecutors%20accuse%20Bankman-Fried%20of%20defrauding%20customers%20and%20investors%20of%20his%20cryptocurrency%20exchange%2C%20FTX%2C%20out%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20witness%20on%20Wednesday%20was%20Eliora%20Katz%2C%20the%20former%20in-house%20lobbyist%20for%20FTX%20US.%20While%20answering%20questions%20about%20company%20communications%2C%20Katz%20maintained%20that%20most%20of%20the%20evidence%20shown%20to%20her%20had%20been%20drafted%20and%20published%20before%20her%20time%20at%20the%20company%20from%20April%20to%20November%20of%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20was%20called%20essentially%20as%20a%20mannequin%20to%20read%20to%20the%20jury%20documents%20in%20evidence%20and%20the%20transcripts%20of%20videotapes%20in%20evidence%2C%20and%20that%20was%20a%20waste%20of%20her%20time%2C%20it%20was%20a%20waste%20of%20the%20jury's%20time%2C%20and%20it%20was%20a%20waste%20of%20everybody%20else's%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Kaplan%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20expect%20different%20behavior%20from%20counsel.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%20in%20the%20day%2C%20the%20prosecution%20called%20Cory%20Gaddis%2C%20a%20records%20custodian%20at%20Google%20who%20flew%20to%20New%20York%20from%20Texas.%20He%20was%20also%20unable%20to%20answer%20most%20of%20the%20questions%