20anonymous%20woman%2C%20applied%20for%20trucking%20positions%20at%20Stevens%20Transport%20between%20April%20and%20June%202023%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic1.squarespace.com%2Fstatic%2F63ffda7f9dcd742dc8620173%2Ft%2F651eca778a549e5101b00616%2F1696516728085%2FRWIT%2BComplaint%2BAgainst%2BStevens%2BTransport.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efiling%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Now%2C%20in%20partnership%20with%20the%20nonprofit%20REAL%20Women%20in%20Trucking%2C%20Peter%20Romer-Friedman's%20law%20firm%20is%20filing%20discrimination%20charges%20against%20Stevens%20Transport%20to%20the%20Equal%20Employment%20Opportunity%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20women%20were%20qualified%20drivers%2C%20none%20were%20hired%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20female%20trainers%20at%20Stevens.%20Because%20the%20company%20has%20a%20same-sex-only%20training%20policy%2C%20they%20said%20they%20could%20not%20hire%20the%20women%20immediately%20%E2%80%94%20even%20though%20Howard%20and%20Streeter%20both%20said%20they%20would%20be%20willing%20to%20be%20trained%20by%20men%2C%20per%20the%20filing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20the%20women%20were%20placed%20on%20a%20monthslong%20%26quot%3Bwaitlist%26quot%3B%20until%20a%20woman%20trainer%20could%20work%20with%20them%2C%20while%20men%20could%20begin%20working%20almost%20immediately%2C%20per%20the%20filing.%20Per%20the%20filing%2C%20other%20women%20applying%20were%20told%20there%20was%20a%20hiring%20freeze%20for%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EConquering%20the%20first%20obstacle%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERomer-Friedman%20told%20Insider%20that%20same-sex%20training%20policies%20are%20one%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bgreatest%20obstacles%26quot%3B%20for%20women%20looking%20for%20trucking%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20long%20as%20there's%20been%20a%20trucking%20industry%20in%20America%2C%20women%20have%20been%20denied%20equal%20opportunity%20in%20that%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20Romer-Friedman%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20an%20important%20first%20step%20to%20dismantling%20the%20systemic%20discrimination%20that%20women%20face%20in%20the%20trucking%20industry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERomer-Friedman%20added%20filing%20with%20the%20EEOC%20is%20the%20first%20step%20in%20a%20process%20that%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20federal%20civil%20rights%20lawsuit%20against%20Stevens%20Transport.%20He%20said%20he%20is%20optimistic%20that%20the%20EEOC%20will%20pursue%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20numbers%20of%20women%20truck%20drivers%20are%20rising%20slowly%2C%20but%20they%20still%20make%20up%20just%20a%20tiny%20fraction%20of%20the%20trucking%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Labor%20Statistics%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bls.gov%2Fcps%2Faa2018%2Fcpsaat39.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%202018%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20women%20made%20up%20just%20about%205.5%25%20of%20the%20full-time%20%26quot%3BDrivers%2Fsales%20workers%20and%20truck%20drivers%26quot%3B%20category%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bls.gov%2Fcps%2Fcpsaat39.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%202022%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20made%20up%20about%206.3%25%20of%20the%20workforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20they%20make%20up%20a%20lower%20percentage%20of%20the%20workforce%2C%20data%20suggest%20they%20are%20both%20safer%20drivers%20and%20less%20likely%20to%20quit%20their%20jobs%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwomen-truck-drivers-better-safer-trucker-shortage-2018-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInsider's%20previous%20reporting%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20rare%20to%20see%20such%20a%20well-documented%20case%20of%20discrimination%2C%26quot%3B%20Romer-Friedman%20said.%20%26quot%3BI've%20practiced%20civil%20rights%20law%20for%20the%20last%2015%20years%2C%20and%20I%20have%20not%20seen%20a%20case%20at%20the%20outset%20where%20the%20conduct%20appears%20to%20be%20so%20crude%20and%20blatant%20as%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ES