trol%20a%20variety%20of%20settings%2C%20audio%20streaming%20services%2C%20and%20smarts.%20It%20worked%20without%20a%20hitch%20over%20two%20weeks%20of%20testing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Design%5C%22%3EThe%20design%20is%20simple%20but%20stylish%20%E2%80%93%20and%20suitably%20hearty%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Samsung%20HW-Q990C%20soundbar%20on%20a%20TV%20console%20shown%20from%20the%20side%20to%20showcase%20the%20firing%20drivers.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652ea89169c17ca46ae86779%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20soundbar%20has%20a%20premium%2C%20sturdy%20build.%3Cp%3ERyan%20Waniata%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20HW-Q990C%20is%20pretty%20massive%2C%20stretching%20over%2048%20inches%20across%20and%20over%20five%20inches%20back%2C%20so%20you'll%20need%20to%20allocate%20proper%20space%20for%20it.%20The%20bar%20is%20basic%20in%20design%20but%20looks%20rather%20elegant%20on%20your%20TV%20console%2C%20and%20the%20construction%20feels%20premium.%20There's%20no%20real%20weak%20spot%20here%2C%20with%20a%20metal%20perforated%20grille%20across%20the%20top%2C%20front%2C%20and%20sides%20revealing%20a%20multitude%20of%20drivers%20beneath.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20the%20Q990B%2C%20the%20Q990C%20offers%20a%20useful%20front-side%20visual%20display%20with%20real%20words%2C%20not%20just%20LEDs.%20That's%20particularly%20handy%20if%20you're%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20if%20you're%20getting%20Dolby%20Atmos%20or%20to%20see%20if%20the%20proper%20input%20is%20selected.%20The%20satellites%20and%20subwoofer%20look%20stylish%20as%20well%2C%20and%20you%20can%20easily%20see%20all%20the%20drivers%20in%20the%20satellite%20speakers%20under%20their%20perforated%20grilles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20included%20remote%20looks%20even%20fancier%2C%20with%20a%20brushed%20metal%20top.%20But%20you%20shouldn't%20need%20the%20remote%20much%20as%20your%20TV%20remote%20and%20the%20Samsung%20app%20account%20for%20most%20functions%20when%20connected%20via%20HDMI%20(but%20not%20if%20you're%20connected%20over%20Wi-Fi).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Performance%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20sound%20is%20balanced%2C%20clear%2C%20and%20incredibly%20immersive%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Samsung%20HW-Q990C%20soundbar%20underneath%20a%20television%20with%20%26quot%3BCaptain%20America%3A%20Civil%20War%26quot%3B%20playing%20on%20its%20screen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652ea95969c17ca46ae8683a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20soundbar's%20movie%20performance%20is%20top-notch%2C%20especially%20when%20listening%20to%20Dolby%20Atmos%20content.%3Cp%3ERyan%20Waniata%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20HW-Q990C%20is%20an%20absolute%20powerhouse%20of%20a%20sound%20system%2C%20capable%20of%20surrounding%20you%20in%20the%20kind%20of%20brain-tricking%20dome%20of%20sound%20for%20which%20Dolby%20Atmos%20was%20created.%20Thanks%20to%20excellent%20control%20and%20an%20almost%20laughable%20number%20of%20speaker%20drivers%2C%20music%20and%20effects%20swirl%20around%20you%20with%20seamless%20fluidity%20and%20precision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20result%20is%20sound%20that's%20not%20only%20exciting%20and%20engaging%20but%20also%20brilliantly%20subtle%20in%20its%20immersion.%20You%20won't%20find%20many%20soundbars%20that%20can%20out-brawl%20the%20Q990C%20and%20its%20650%2B%20watts%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20sheer%20power%2C%20but%20it's%20arguably%20even%20better%20when%20rendering%20the%20more%20granular%20moments%2C%20from%20a%20rainstorm%20overhead%20to%20an%20echoey%20voice%20in%20a%20splashy%20hallway.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20collage%20of%20upfiring%2C%20front-firing%2C%20and%20side-firing%20speaker%20drivers%2C%20including%20the%20satellite%20speakers%20at%20the%20rear%2C%20provide%20pinpoint%20accuracy%20when%20working%20in%20concert%20with%20the%20main%20bar%20for%20Dolby%20Atmos%20%26quot%3Bsound%20objects.%26quot%3B%20That%20means%20little%20effects%2C%20like%20a%20buzzing%20fly%20or%20a%20whirling%20helicopter%20set%20miles%20above%20the%20action%2C%20sound%20incredibly%20realistic.%20Each%20effect%20feels%20perfectly%20placed%20within%20the%20soundstage%2C%20seeming%20to%20kick%20in%20an%20almost%20primal%20instinct%20that%20tricks%20you%20into%20believing%20you're%20there.%20In%20short%2C%20the%20Q990C%20is%20a%20cinematic%20wizard.%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20side-by-side%20shot%20ofa%20Samsung%20Q990C%20subwoofer%20and%20Q990C%20satellite%20speaker.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652eb3aa211def8ed8374833%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222249%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20system's%20subwoodfer%20(left)%20and%20satellite%20speakers%20(right)%20help%20to%20expand%20its%20soundstage%20and%20bass.%3Cp%3ERyan%20Waniata%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20true%20whether%20the%20Q990C%20is%20connected%20over%20Wi-Fi%20with%20a%20newer%20Samsung%20TV%20or%20via%20the%20traditional%20HDMI%20connection.%20The%20Q-Sympony%20feature%2C%20which%20plays%20audio%20through%20the%20bar%20and%20your%20Samsung%20TV%20speakers%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20can%20provide%20an%20even%20broader%20sense%20of%20space%20and%20directionality%20for%20some%20content%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20necessary%20to%20get%20the%20most%20out%20of%20the%20system.%20Whatever%20TV%20you%20own%2C%20the%20Q990C%20raises%20the%20audio%20stakes%20significantly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20when%20you're%20not%20getting%20lost%20in%20Ant-Man's%20miniature%20world%20or%20deep%20beneath%20the%20waves%20of%20a%20neon%20coral%20reef%20in%20Netflix's%20%26quot%3BOur%20Planet%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Q990C%20proves%20Samsung%20knows%20audio%20tuning.%20The%20sound%20profile%20is%20warm%20yet%20detailed%2C%20elevating%20everything%20from%20the%20velvety%20purr%20of%20Bucky's%20Harley%20Davidson%20in%20%26quot%3BCaptain%20America%3A%20Civil%20War%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20flashy%20dialogue%20in%20Amazon%20Prime's%20%26quot%3BGood%20Omens.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20this%20is%20still%20a%20soundbar%2C%20and%20at%20times%20you%20can%20hear%20it%20over-correcting%20with%20software%20to%20limit%20distortion%20or%20trending%20toward%20a%20boxier%2C%20sharper%20sound%20in%20the%20brightest%20productions.%20Those%20moments%20are%20in%20the%20minority%2C%20though%2C%20even%20for%20music%20playback.%20The%20bar%20and%20the%20subwoofer%20work%20in%20concert%20to%20provide%20punchy%20and%20well-balanced%20sound%2C%20from%20jazz%20to%20hip-hop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20of%20the%20sub%2C%20it%20has%20plenty%20of%20boom%20yet%20it's%20easily%20tamed%20with%20the%20remote's%20woofer%20key%2C%20to%20render%20lower%20frequencies%20with%20smooth%20musicality.%20We'd%20still%20prefer%20a%20similarly%20priced%20bookshelf%20speaker%20system%20for%20music%20playback%20on%20the%20whole.%20But%20the%20Q990C%20handles%20instruments%20with%20care%2C%20from%20flashy%20guitars%20and%20synths%20to%20reedy%20horns%20and%20strings%2C%20offering%20more%20than%20enough%20groove%20and%20flow%20to%20serve%20as%20your%20primary%20audio%20device.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Features%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20bar%20offers%20good%20features%2C%20with%20a%20few%20exceptions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Samsung%20HW-Q990C%20soundbar%20underside%2C%20showing%20the%20input%20section.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652ea8cf6561dd877e7c6252%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETwo%20HDMI%20inputs%20are%20included%20to%20connect%20to%20other%20devices%2C%20but%20they%20don't%20support%20120Hz%20or%20VRR%20passthrough%20with%20game%20consoles.%3Cp%3ERyan%20Waniata%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EYou'll%20get%20%3Cem%3Enearly%3C%2Fem%3E%20every%20feature%20you%20could%20want%20with%20the%20HW-Q990C%2C%20including%20an%20array%20of%20settings%20and%20smarts%2C%20along%20with%20support%20for%20virtually%20every%20major%20audio%20format.%20That%20includes%20the%20big%20ones%20like%20Dolby%20Atmos%20and%20Dolby%20TrueHD%20as%20well%20as%20their%20DTS%20counterparts%20like%20DTS-HD%20Master%20Audio%20and%20DTS%3AX%2C%20the%20main%203D-audio%20rival%20to%20Dolby%20Atmos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmartThings%20makes%20the%20software%20experience%20pretty%20intuitive%2C%20with%20the%20ability%20to%20adjust%20nearly%20all%20settings%20from%20your%20mobile%20device.%20Samsung%20also%20offers%20features%20like%20SpaceFit%20Sound%2C%20designed%20to%20adjust%20the%20audio%20to%20your%20room%20automatically%2C%20and%20Adaptive%20Sound%20mode%2C%20which%20does%20an%20impressive%20job%20of%20optimizing%20the%20audio%20for%20whatever%20you%20play%20in%20real-time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETinkerers%20will%20find%20a%20full%20multi-band%20EQ%20when%20using%20the%20Standard%20sound%20mode%2C%20and%20individual%20channel%20settings%20let%20you%20do%20things%20like%20adjust%20the%20center%20or%20upfiring%20speakers%20to%20fine-tune%20their%20performance.%20(Samsung%20hides%20that%20last%20setting%20under%20the%20triple%20dots%20at%20the%20app's%20right%20corner%20under%20Device%20Settings.)%20You%20can%20also%20make%20most%20adjustments%20with%20the%20included%20remote%2C%20though%20this%20is%20definitely%20a%20more%20arduous%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%2