20Biden%20was%20in%20Israel%20and%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20need%20that%20diplomacy%20to%20play%20out%E2%80%9D.%20She%20also%20said%20that%20the%20draft%20resolution%20did%20not%20mention%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20self-defence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20the%2087%3Cspan%3Eth%20%3C%2Fspan%3Etime%20that%20the%20US%20had%20cast%20a%20veto%20in%20the%20UNSC.%20More%20than%20half%20of%20them%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FSCProcedure%2Fstatus%2F1714658796922876193%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E47%20vetoes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20were%20related%20to%20issues%20in%20the%20West%20Asian%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20General%20Assembly%20will%20now%20have%20to%20convene%20in%20a%20formal%20meeting%20to%20discuss%20the%20veto%20cast%20by%20the%20US%20within%20ten%20days.%20This%20mandate%20stems%20from%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpress.un.org%2Fen%2F2022%2Fga12417.doc.htm%5C%22%3EUNGA%20resolution%3C%2Fa%3E%20introduced%20by%20Western%20nations%20and%20ratified%20in%20April%202022%2C%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Fdepts%2Fdhl%2Fresguide%2Fscact_veto_table_en.htm%5C%22%3ERussian%20veto%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20prevented%20the%20Security%20Council%20from%20taking%20any%20action%20after%20the%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmid%20escalating%20tensions%20in%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20conflict%2C%20two%20draft%20resolutions%20were%20shared%20among%20members%20of%20the%20UNSC.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Russian%20draft%20resolution%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fisrael-hamas-un-resolutions-russia-brazil-c601d6aefe9d853428a485c9b6011830%5C%22%3Epresented%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Monday%20night%20but%20fell%20short%20of%20the%20nine%20votes%20needed%20for%20adoption.%20Only%20four%20countries%20%E2%80%93%20China%2C%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%2C%20Mozambique%2C%20and%20Gabon%20%E2%80%93%20voted%20in%20favour%2C%20while%20six%20countries%20abstained.%20The%20US%2C%20Britain%2C%20France%2C%20and%20Japan%20opted%20for%20abstention.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%20morning%2C%20the%20Brazilian%20draft%20resolution%20was%20submitted%20to%20the%20Council.%20It%20had%20undergone%20significant%20language%20revisions%20proposed%20by%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%2C%20France%2C%20and%20the%20UK%20since%20the%20initial%20draft%20circulated%20on%20October%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.securitycouncilreport.org%2Fwhatsinblue%2F2023%2F10%2Fthe-middle-east-including-the-palestinian-question-vote-on-competing-draft-resolutions.php%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESecurity%20Council%20Report%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20initial%20draft%20text%20condemned%20the%20%E2%80%9Cterrorist%20attack%20by%20Hamas%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20was%20changed%20to%20a%20much%20stronger%20%E2%80%9Cunequivocally%20reject%5Bing%5D%20and%20condemn%5Bing%5D%20the%20heinous%20terrorist%20attacks%20by%20Hamas%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20taking%20of%20civilian%20hostages%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20final%20text.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20call%20for%20%E2%80%9Can%20immediate%20ceasefire%E2%80%9D%20was%20removed%20and%20the%20resolution%20only%20called%20for%20the%20establishment%20of%20%E2%80%9Chumanitarian%20pauses%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20violence.%20The%20mention%20of%20Israel%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20demand%20for%20immediate%20withdrawal%20of%20the%20October%2013%20order%20for%20Palestinians%20in%20North%20Gaza%20to%20leave%20their%20homes%20was%20also%20toned%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EUS%20vetoes%20Security%20Council%20resolution%20that%20would%20have%20called%20for%20%E2%80%9Chumanitarian%20pauses%E2%80%9D%20to%20deliver%20lifesaving%20aid%20to%20millions%20in%20Gaza%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFavor%3A%2012%20(Albania%2C%20Brazil%2C%20China%2C%20Ecuador%2C%20France%2C%20Gabon%2C%20Ghana%2C%20Japan%2C%20Malta%2C%20Mozambique%2C%20Switzerland%2CUAE)%3Cbr%3E%20Against%3A%201%20(US)%3Cbr%3E%20Abstain%3A%202%20Russia%2C%20UK%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fy4tiAbRMUQ%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fy4tiAbRMUQ%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20UN%20News%20(%40UN_News_Centre)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUN_News_Centre%2Fstatus%2F1714649681521791305%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2018%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20UNSC%20assembled%20in%20New%20York%20this%20morning%2C%20Russia%20tabled%20two%20amendments%20to%20the%20draft%20resolution%2C%20which%20asked%20for%20language%20calling%20for%20full%20ceasefire%2C%20stopping%20attacks%20on%20civilians%20and%20lifting%20the%20blockade.%20Both%20of%20them%20failed%20as%20they%20failed%20to%20get%20the%20nine%20votes%20required%20as%20per%20guidelines.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20sole%20Arab%20member%20of%20the%20UNSC%2C%20the%20UAE%2C%20said%20that%20the%20sufferings%20in%20Gaza%20made%20a%20mockery%20of%20international%20law.%20The%20UAE%20had%20normalised%20ties%20with%20Israel%20after%20signing%20the%20Abraham%20accords.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20strongly%20condemned%20Hamas%20for%20the%20incursion%20which%20killed%20hundreds%20of%20Israelis%20on%20October%207.%20But%2C%20it%20has%20also%20pointed%20fingers%20at%20Israel%20for%20being%20behind%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fdays-before-catastrophic-bombing-of-gaza-hospital-israel-had-fired-rocket-ordered-its-evacuation%5C%22%3Eexplosion%20at%20Al%20Ahli%20hospital%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday%20night%20which%20killed%20hundreds%20of%20Palestinians%20sheltering%20inside%20from%20Israeli%20airstrikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Security%20Council%20failed%20to%20adopt%20a%20resolution%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20UAE%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FGlobalActionPW%2Fstatus%2F1714660175699910799%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Ewarned%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20hope%20generated%20by%20the%20Abraham%20Accords%2