of%20the%20world%20to%20discuss%20political%20issues%20and%20takes%20opposing%20views%20than%20his%20daughter%20to%20encourage%20her%20to%20read%20more%20so%20she%20can%20form%20a%20strong%20argument%20against%20him.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3EHajer%20Sharief%2C%20a%20Libyan%20peace%20and%20human%20rights%20activist%2C%20introduces%20a%20simple%20yet%20transformative%20idea%20%E2%80%93%20parents%20can%20teach%20their%20children%20about%20political%20functioning%20by%20giving%20them%20a%20say%20in%20how%20their%20households%20are%20run%2C%20in%20the%20form%20of%20regular%20family%20meetings%20where%20everyone%20has%20an%20equal%20say%20and%20learns%20to%20negotiate%20their%20demands%20and%20put%20across%20their%20feelings.%20This%20way%20young%20people%2C%20both%20boys%20and%20girls%2C%20learn%20similar%20skills%20and%20have%20the%20same%20space%20to%20discuss%20and%20deliberate.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Fol%3E%20%3Col%20start%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ECreate%20structured%20opportunities%20for%20girls%20to%20lead%20and%20highlight%20women%20politicians%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESchools%20play%20an%20important%20role%20in%20supporting%20the%20political%20development%20of%20young%20children%20and%20through%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F13819%2Funleash-dreams-india-youth-loan-vocational-training-skills-milaap%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esuch%20activities%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20can%20increase%20their%20interest%20in%20civic%20action.%20%E2%80%98Action%20civics%E2%80%99%2C%20where%20students%20learn%20important%20civic%20skills%20and%20then%20lead%20their%20own%20initiatives%2C%20has%20been%20shown%20to%20increase%20a%20student%E2%80%99s%20sense%20of%20civic%20competence%20and%20agency%20(LeCompte%20et%20al.%2C%202020).%C2%A0%3Cbr%3EKuviraa%E2%80%99s%20flagship%20%E2%80%98Ambassador%20Program%E2%80%99%20gives%20girls%20an%20opportunity%20to%20participate%20in%20mock%20elections%20through%20a%20campai