n-wife-son-abdullah-7-year-jail-fake-birth-certificate-case-8988994%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20the%20past%20one%20month%2C%20this%20is%20the%20fourth%20case%20in%20which%20Azam%20Khan%20has%20been%20convicted.%20This%20is%20also%20the%20second%20conviction%20of%20former%20MLA%20Abdullah%20Azam%20Khan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EArun%20Parkash%20Saxena%2C%20a%20former%20district%20government%20counsel%2C%20who%20was%20representing%20the%20prosecution%2C%20told%20PTI%2C%C2%A0%E2%80%9CAfter%20the%20court%20verdict%2C%20the%20trio%20was%20taken%20into%20judicial%20custody%20and%20will%20be%20sent%20to%20the%20jail%20from%20the%20court%20itself.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20information%20register%20(FIR)%20in%20the%20case%20was%20lodged%20by%20a%20resident%2C%20Akash%20Saxena%20(who%20is%20now%20a%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20MLA)%2C%20at%20the%20Ganj%20police%20station%20in%20Rampur%2C%20on%20January%203%2C%202019.%20He%20had%20alleged%20that%20Khan%20and%20his%20wife%20helped%20their%20son%20obtain%20two%20fake%20date%20of%20birth%20certificates%20%E2%80%93%20one%20from%20Lucknow%20and%20another%20from%20Rampur.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20charge-sheet%2C%20in%20the%20certificate%20issued%20by%20the%20Rampur%20municipality%2C%20Abdullah%20Azam%E2%80%99s%20date%20of%20birth%20was%20mentioned%20as%20January%201%2C%201993.%20The%20other%20certificate%20said%20he%20was%20born%20in%20Lucknow%20on%20September%2030%2C%201990.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAbdullah%20is%20accused%20of%20using%20the%20first%20one%20for%20his%20passport%20and%20for%20travels%20abroad%2C%20while%20the%20second%20one%20was%20used%20for%20government%20records%20and%20for%20getting%20affiliation%20with%20Jauhar%20University%2C%20%3Cem%3EIE%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20convicted%20under%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC)%20sections%20420%20(cheating%20and%20dishonestly%20inducing%20delivery%20of%20property)%2C%20467%20(forgery%20of%20valuable%20security%2C%20will%2C%20etc.)%2C%20468%20(forgery%20for%20purpose%20of%20cheating)%2C%20471%20(using%20as%20genuine%20a%20forged%201%5Bdocument%20or%20electronic%20record%5D)%20and%20120-B%20(criminal%20conspiracy).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2026%2C%202020%2C%20Azam%20Khan%2C%20his%20wife%20and%20son%20had%20surrendered%20before%20a%20local%20court%20in%20Rampur%2C%20over%20their%20connection%20with%20the%20case.%20Later%2C%20all%20three%20obtained%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20BJP%20assumed%20power%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20in%202017%2C%20Azam%20Khan%20has%20faced%2081%20cases%20filed%20against%20him%20in%20Rampur%20on%20multiple%20charges%2C%20such%20as%20land-grabbing%2C%20cheating%2C%20and%20criminal%20trespass.%20Additionally%2C%20Azam%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20wife%2C%20Tanzeen%20Fatima%2C%20and%20his%20son%2C%20Abdullah%20Azam%2C%20have%20been%20implicated%20in%20some%20of%20these%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20a%20Rampur%20court%20sentenced%20Azam%20Khan%20to%20two%20years%20in%20prison%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frampur-court-azam-khan-hate-speech-conviction%5C%22%3Ehate%20speech%20case%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20election.%20Subsequently%2C%20the%20court%20granted%20him%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697633426000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18180729%2Fimage-1402.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fazam-khan-his-wife-and-son-given-7-year-jail-term-in-fake-birth-certificate-case%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20FIR%20in%20the%20case%20was%20lodged%20by%20a%20resident%2C%20Akash%20Saxena%20(who%20is%20now%20a%20BJP%20MLA)%2C%20in%20Rampur%2C%20on%20January%203%2C%202019.%20He%20alleged%20that%20Khan%20and%20his%20wife%20got%20two%20birth%20certificates%20made%20for%20their%20son%20Abdullah%20Azam%20Khan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A40%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fazam-khan-his-wife-and-son-given-7-year-jail-term-in-fake-birth-certificate-case%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tory%20MP%20accuses%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20of%20'war%20crimes'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697632020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F10%2F768x432%2Fskynews-crispin-blunt-conservative_6323893.jpg%3F20231016231523%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Ftory-mp-accuses-israeli-and-hamas-of-war-crimes-in-israel-and-gaza-12986993%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Tory%20MP%20has%20accused%20both%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20of%20having%20%26quot%3Bcommitted%20war%20crimes%26quot%3B%20as%20part%20of%20the%20current%20conflict.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A234%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Ftory-mp-accuses-israeli-and-hamas-of-war-crimes-in-israel-and-gaza-12986993%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Ftory-mp-accuses-israeli-and-hamas-of-war-crimes-in-israel-and-gaza-12986993%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Ftory-mp-accuses-israeli-and-hamas-of-war-crimes-in-israel-and-gaza-12986993%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indo-Nepal%20Border%3A%20Schools%20Run%20by%20Hindutva%20Outfit%20Teach%20Kids%20to%20'Identify%20Enemies%20of%20Hindus'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18164010%2FThe-Wire-44.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELakhimpur%20Kheri%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Palia%20Kalan%20is%20a%20village%20of%20about%2050%2C000%20people%20located%20in%20the%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20district%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20It%20is%2040%20kilometres%20away%20from%20Dhangadhi%2C%20the%20first%20village%20one%20reaches%20in%20Nepal%20if%20you%20cross%20the%20border%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20Palia%20Kalan%20is%20home%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.britannica.com%2Ftopic%2FTharu%5C%22%3ETharu%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20indigenous%20tribal%20community.%20The%20tribe%20is%20spread%20across%20the%20border%20districts%20sitting%20on%20the%20Indo-Nepal%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEvery%20day%20around%2010%20am%2C%20Tharu%20girls%20and%20women%20in%20Palia%20Kalan%20queue%20up%20to%20go%20to%20a%20one-teacher%20school.%20This%20school%20is%20run%20by%20the%20Ekal%20Vidyalaya%20Foundation%20(EVF)%2C%20which%20offers%20general%20education%20and%20vocational%20classes%20free%20of%20cost%20for%20children%20aged%20five%20to%2014%20from%20any%20caste%20or%20religion.%20EVF%20USA%2C%20which%20runs%20these%20schools%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthediplomat.com%2F2023%2F09%2Fin-india-hindutva-schools-are-indoctrinating-poor-children%2F%5C%22%3Elinked%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20and%20the%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20(VHP)%2C%20USA.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EClasses%20at%20Ekal%20include%20a%20mix%20of%20children%20from%20all%20segments%20of%20the%20village%3A%20Hindu%20upper%20castes%2C%20lower%20castes%2C%20tribals%2C%20and%20Muslims.%20Since%201989%2C%20Ekal%20claims%20to%20have%20educated%20over%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ekal.org%2Fin%2Four-work%2Feducation%5C%22%3E10%20million%20students%20in%2080%2C000%20villages%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20tribal%20areas%20in%20India.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ekal.org%2Fin%2Four-work%2Feducation%5C%22%3EAs%20of%20June%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20had%2017%2C091%20Ekal%20schools%2C%20where%20more%20than%205%2C16%2C562%20students%20were%20enrolled.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98War%20against%20enemies%20of%20Hinduism%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Palia%20Kalan%2C%20Sanju%20Kumari%2C%20a%2028-year-old%20woman%20from%20the%20Tharu%20tribe%2C%20talks%20very%20fondly%20of%20%E2%80%9CHinduism%E2%80%9D.%20She%20has%20attended%20various%20women%E2%80%99s%20meet-ups%20of%20the%20RSS%20in%20Lucknow.%20%E2%80%9COur%20people%20(Tharu%20tribe)%20have%20been%20away%20from%20Hinduism%20for%20decades%2C%20but%20now%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20RSS%2C%20we%20are%20realising%20the%20importance%20of%20Hinduism%20and%20the%20war%20that%20should%20be%20waged%20against%20the%20enemies%20of%20the%20Hindu%20religion%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kumari%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20class%20of%2018%20women%20students%2C%20Kumari%20teaches%20them%20Hindu%20prayers%20and%20morals%2C%20how%20to%20stitch%20clothes%2C%20and%20who%20the%20%E2%80%9Cactual%20enemies%20of%20Hinduism%E2%80%9D%20are.%20For%20a%20year%20now%2C%20Kumari%20has%20been%20educating%20women%20up%20to%20the%20age%20of%2030%20about%20the%20dangers%20Islam%20and%20Christianity%20can%20pose.%20Kumari%20and%20Chandravati%20Rana%20%E2%80%93%20another%20Tharu%20woman%20who%20is%20also%20associated%20with%20the%20RSS%20%E2%80%93%20have%20been%20teaching%20women%20about%20%E2%80%98Love%20Jihad%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20an%20Islamophobic%20conspiracy%20suggesting%20that%20Muslim%20men%20lure%20Hindu%20women%20into%20marrying%20them%20only%20to%20convert%20them%20to%20Islam%20and%20to%20establish%20demographic%20dominance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18164129%2FEV3-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18164129%2FEV3-1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18164129%2FEV3-1-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18164129%2FEV3-1-1024x576.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-680668%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESanju%20Kumari%20(left)%20and%20Chandravati%20Rana%20at%20the%20Ekal%20Sewing%20Centre%20in%20Palia%20Kalan.%20Photo%3A%20Tarushi%20Aswani%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDid%20you%20not%20see%20what%20that%20Muslim%20man%20did%20to%20Shraddha%20(Walkar)%3F%20How%20he%20chopped%20her%20to%20pieces%3F%20Muslim%20men%20cannot%20be%20trusted%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kumari%20told%20her%20students%2C%20who%20are%20as%20young%20as%20seven%20%E2%80%93%20referring%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2Fcourt-frames-charges-in-shraddha-walkar-murder-case-8600806%2F%5C%22%3Ecase%20of%20Shraddha%20Walkar%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20was%20murdered%20by%20her%20live-in%20partner%2C%20Aaftab%20Amin%20Poonawala.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKumari%20and%20Rana%20have%20also%20been%20fighting%20local%20pastors%20who%20try%20to%20spread%20the%20message%20of%20the%20Bible%20in%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri.%20They%20claim%20to%20have%20burnt%20copies%20of%20the%20Bible%20to%20stop%20this.%20Their%20affiliation%20with%20the%20organisation%20gives%20them%20strength%2C%20they%20say.%20Although%20they%20work%20as%20educators%20and%20are%20paid%20less%2C%20their%20passion%20for%20the%20propagation%20of%20Hinduism%20does%20not%20fade%2C%20they%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETharu%20women%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20most%20men%20from%20the%20tribe%20are%20alcoholics%20and%20some%20travel%20outside%20of%20the%20village%20looking%20for%20work.%20Troubled%20by%20unemployment%2C%20Tharu%20women%20are%20becoming%20part%20of%20the%20Ekal%20Vidyalaya%20Foundation%20to%20earn%20whatever%20little%20is%20handed%20to%20them.%20This%2C%20they%20say%2C%20gives%20them%20the%20chance%20to%20teach%20Hinduism%20and%20earn%20at%20the%20same%20time.%C2%A0According%20to%20estimates%2C%20there%20are%20about%201%2C50%2C000%20Tharu%20people%20in%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Bihar%2C%20which%20share%20a%20border%20with%20Nepal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18164451%2FEV2-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18164451%2FEV2-1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18164451%2FEV2-1-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18164451%2FEV2-1-1024x576.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-680674%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ETharu%20girls%20and%20women%20at%20the%20Ekal%20Centre%20in%20Palia%20Kalan.%20Photo%3A%20Tarushi%20Aswani%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EBoth%20Kumari%20and%20Rana%20said%20that%20they%20motivate%20other%20Tharu%20women%20from%20neighbouring%20villages%2C%20such%20as%20Balera%2C%20Beldandi%2C%20Bander%20Bharari%2C%20Dhuskeya%2C%20Pachpeda%2C%20and%20Dhyanpur%2C%20to%20attend%20the%20classes%20at%20Ekal%20Vidyalaya.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRamnagar%20is%20the%20only%20village%20which%20has%20no%20students%20here%2C%20only%20Muslims%20live%20there.%20A%20few%20of%20them%20students%20came%20here%20once%2C%20but%20they%20refused%20to%20sing%20Hindu%20prayer%20songs%2C%20so%20it%20is%20useless%20for%20them%20to%20attend%20classes%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Kumari.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndoctrinated%20to%20hate%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20abandoned%20temple%20in%20Palia%20Kalan%2C%20Janaki%20Devi%2C%20a%20priestess%2C%20has%20been%20asking%20Hindus%20to%20re-establish%20the%20sanctity%20of%20the%20temple%20by%20joining%20her%20in%20praying%20to%20deities%20and%20acting%20upon%20what%20Hinduism%20truly%20advocates.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20first%20came%20here%2C%20this%20temple%20had%20evil%20spirits.%20I%20cleansed%20the%20temple%20and%20now%20it%20has%20become%20a%20%3Cem%3EDharamshala%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20the%20needy%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Devi.%20She%20also%20adds%20that%20ill%20persons%20who%20stay%20at%20the%20temple%20magically%20heal%20after%20chanting%20%3Cem%3Emantras%3C%2Fem%3E.%20While%20Devi%20is%20not%20associated%20with%20the%20RSS%20or%20EVF%2C%20she%20subscribes%20to%20the%20ideology%20of%20Hindutva%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18164305%2FEV4-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18164305%2FEV4-1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18164305%2FEV4-1-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18164305%2FEV4-1-1024x576.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-680669%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPriestess%20Janaki%20Devi%20at%20the%20temple%20in%20Palia%20Kalan.%20Photo%3A%20Tarushi%20Aswani%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EDevi%20fully%20echoes%20the%20idea%20that%20Ekal%20advocates%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20more%20training.%20The%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20should%20also%20train%20women%20to%20defend%20themselves%20and%20fight%20against%20those%20corrupting%20Hindu%20minds.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CHindutva%20ko%20aage%20badhaane%20ke%20liye%20prayaas%20karna%20padhega%2C%20yahan%20buhot%20log%20issai%20dharam%20mein%20jaa%20rhay%20hain.%20Humein%20yeh%20rokna%20hoga.%20Chahe%20granth%20ki%20padhaai%20ho%20yaan%20danda%20chalana%2C%20Hinduon%20ko%20sab%20aana%20chahiye%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Hindus%20have%20to%20put%20up%20with%20struggle%20to%20move%20forward.%20Several%20people%20here%20are%20converting%20to%20Christianity.%20We%20have%20to%20stop%20this.%20Whether%20it%20is%20through%20reading%20Hindu%20scriptures%20or%20through%20force.%20Hindus%20should%20know%20everything)%2C%E2%80%9D%20Devi%20argues.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20propagating%20Hindutva%2C%20Devi%20undertakes%20a%20%E2%80%98noble%E2%80%99%20task%20every%20Friday.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20disciples%20and%20I%20make%20sure%20to%20blast%20%3Cem%3Ebhajans%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20full%20volume%20when%20they%20(Muslims)%20read%20%3Cem%3Eazaan%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20Friday%20namaz.%20This%20is%20my%20way%20to%20stop%20Islam.%20But%20Christians%20are%20out%20of%20control%2C%20they%20give%20money%2C%20property%2C%20and%20alcohol%20to%20convert%20Hindus%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Devi.%20%E2%80%9CSanatanis%20are%20precious%2C%20they%20should%20be%20trained%20by%20the%20Sangh.%20They%20are%20the%20true%20fighters%20in%20the%20cause.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKumari%20and%20Rana%20agree%20with%20Devi.%20They%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20this%20%E2%80%98training%E2%80%99%20that%20Devi%20suggests%20is%20needed%20to%20keep%20the%20population%20of%20Christians%20and%20Muslims%20under%20check.%20They%20regularly%20consult%20Devi%20and%20take%20her%20suggestions%20to%20the%20local%20RSS%20affiliates%20who%20also%20contact%20Devi%20frequently%20concerning%20mass%20conversion%20conspiracies%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMuslims%20on%20the%20Indo-Nepal%20border%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20met%20with%20Mahender%20Yadav%2C%20the%20supervisor%20of%20Ekal%20schools%20in%20Sitapur%20district.%20Yadav%2C%20who%20took%20Kumari%20and%20Rana%20under%20his%20wings%2C%20believes%20that%20Muslims%20and%20Christians%20%E2%80%9Cneed%20to%20be%20shown%20their%20rightful%20place%20in%20society%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20can%20either%20accept%20Hindu%20supremacy%20or%20convert%20to%20Hinduism.%20Ekal%20prepares%20children%20to%20identify%20enemies%20of%20Hinduism%20at%20an%20early%20stage%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnder%20Yadav%2C%20430%20Ekal%20schools%20and%20institutions%20further%20the%20agenda%20of%20radicalising%20students.%20But%20the%20propaganda%20that%20these%20schools%20further%20through%20Tharus%20travels%20beyond%20classrooms.%20Due%20to%20the%20presence%20of%20these%20schools%2C%20Muslims%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20villages%20that%20border%20Nepal%20feel%20vulnerable%20with%20children%20being%20indoctrinated%20to%20hate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBrij%20Bihari%2C%20a%20social%20activist%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Sitapur%20district%2C%20feels%20that%20Tharus%20are%20being%20%E2%80%9Cused%20as%20foot%20soldiers%20in%20the%20border%20districts%20to%20channelise%20Hindutva%20sentiment%E2%80%9D.%20Bihari%20also%20views%20this%20as%20a%20dangerous%20trend%20which%20could%20jeopardise%20the%20lives%20of%20Christians%20and%20Muslims%20along%20the%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20new%20schools%20of%20%E2%80%98hate%E2%80%99%20coming%20up%20every%20day%2C%20Muslims%20like%20advocate%20Pervez%20Iqbal%20feel%20that%20his%20community%20is%20staring%20at%20genocide.%20Iqbal%2C%20who%20is%20a%20local%20activist%20from%20Shravasti%2C%20feels%20that%20Hindutva%20groups%20are%20gaining%20stronger%20ground%20in%20the%20border%20districts%20ever%20since%202014%2C%20and%20even%20more%20since%202019%20%E2%80%93%20coinciding%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIqbal%E2%80%99s%20neighbour%2C%20a%2060-year-old%20Muslim%20man%2C%20Rabiullah%2C%20feels%20that%20with%20tribals%20siding%20with%20Hindutva%20groups%2C%20Muslims%20would%20be%20forced%20to%20leave%20their%20homes%20merely%20for%20being%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CYeh%20log%20kabhi%20bhi%20nikaal%20denge%20humein%2C%20phir%20itni%20mehnat%20ka%20ghar%20do%20paise%20mein%20bech%20kar%20bhaagna%20parhega%2C%20yahan%20haalaat%20waisay%20bhi%20election%20ke%20time%20buhot%20garam%20rehte%20hain%3C%2Fem%3E%20(These%20people%20can%20kick%20us%20out%20any%20moment.%20We%20will%20have%20to%20sell%20our%20hard-earned%20homes%20in%20distress%20and%20migrate.%20As%20it%20is%2C%20during%20election%20time%2C%20the%20situation%20is%20hot%20to%20handle%20here)%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rabiullah%2C%20who%20has%20lived%20in%20Shravasti%20all%20his%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697631611000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18164010%2FThe-Wire-44.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Findo-nepal-border-schools-hindutva-outfit-indoctrinate%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Ekal%20Vidyalaya%20Foundation%2C%20which%20is%20linked%20to%20RSS%20and%20VHP%2C%20is%20indoctrinating%20women%20and%20children%20of%20a%20the%20Tharu%20tribal%20community.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Findo-nepal-border-schools-hindutva-outfit-indoctrinate%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Power%20Bills%20Rising%20While%20Adani%20Takes%20Money%20from%20India's%20Poorest%3A%20Rahul%20Gandhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18164052%2FUntitled-design-2-3.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Congress%20MP%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20on%20Wednesday%20(October%2018)%20accused%20the%20Adani%20group%20of%20over-invoicing%20coal%20prices%20and%20taking%20money%20out%20of%20the%20pockets%20of%20poor%20people%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Gandhi%20cited%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fadani-coal-imports-over-pricing-customers-overcharged-fuel-ft%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereport%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Eby%20London-based%20financial%20daily%2C%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3ETimes%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20had%20in%20a%20detailed%20investigation%20last%20week%2C%20titled%2C%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F7aadb3d7-4a03-44ba-a01e-8ddd8bce29ed%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20mystery%20of%20the%20Adani%20coal%20imports%20that%20quietly%20doubled%20in%20value%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20found%20that%20Adani%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20country%E2%80%99s%20largest%20private%20coal%20importer%2C%20has%20been%20inflating%20fuel%20costs%E2%80%9D%20leading%20to%20%E2%80%9Cmillions%20of%20Indian%20consumers%20and%20businesses%20overpaying%20for%20electricity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20story%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3ETimes%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20one%20of%20the%20pre-eminent%20financial%20newspapers%20in%20the%20world%2C%20where%20they%20are%20clearly%20stating%20that%20%E2%80%9CAdani%20and%20the%20mysterious%20coal%20price%20rises%E2%80%9D.%20Mr.%20Adani%20buys%20coal%20in%20Indonesia%20and%20by%20the%20time%20coal%20arrives%20in%20India%2C%20its%20prices%20doubles%20and%20he%20has%20taken%20approximately%20Rs%2012%2C000%20crores%20from%20the%20pockets%20of%20the%20poorest%20people%20in%20India.%20Our%20electricity%20prices%20are%20going%20up%20and%20Adani%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20over-invoicing%20while%20taking%20money%20from%20the%20pockets%20of%20the%20poorest%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhi%20said%20that%20while%20the%20%3Cem%3EFT%3C%2Fem%3E%20story%20would%20%E2%80%9Cbring%20down%20any%20government%E2%80%9D%2C%20Indian%20media%20has%20not%20picked%20up%20the%20story.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CInteresting%20question%20to%20me%E2%80%A6the%3Cem%3E%20Financial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20a%20huge%20story.%20This%20story%20would%20bring%20down%20any%20government.%20This%20is%20direct%20theft%20by%20a%20man%2C%20who%20has%20been%20protected%20again%2C%20and%20again%2C%20and%20again%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India.%20And%20the%20surprising%20thing%20is%2C%20not%20a%20single%20Indian%20newspaper%20is%20interested%20in%20picking%20up%20the%20story%2C%20not%20a%20single%20media%20channel%20is%20interested%20in%20picking%20up%20the%20story%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20giving%20electricity%20subsidies%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20and%20going%20to%20do%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20while%20we%20are%20giving%20electricity%20subsidies%2C%20Mr.%20Adani%20is%20over%20invoicing%20coal%20and%20stealing%20directly%20from%20the%20people%20of%20India%2C%20and%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20understand%20why%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20comment%20on%20this.%20This%20cannot%20happen%20without%20the%20protection%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India.%20It%20is%20impossible.%20So%2C%20the%20question%20is%3A%20why%20is%20there%20no%20action%20being%20taken%20on%20this%20gentleman%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Will%20definitely%20get%20it%20done%2C%20why%20not%3F%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%20in%20January%2C%20US%20short-seller%20Hindenburg%20Research%E2%80%99s%20report%20alleged%20stock%20market%20manipulation%20by%20the%20Adani%20group%20and%20also%20raised%20questions%20about%20regulatory%20mechanisms%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStock%20market%20watchdog%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI)%20came%20under%20fire%20even%20when%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20expert%20committee%20pointed%20to%20certain%20changes%20in%20rules%20that%20may%20have%20made%20it%20easier%20for%20Adani%20to%20escape%20scrutiny.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Adani%20group%20has%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businesstoday.in%2Flatest%2Fcorporate%2Fstory%2Fadani-group-hits-out-at-financial-times-for-trying-to-tarnish-reputation-financially-destabilise-company-401342-2023-10-10%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edenied%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20charges%20and%20said%20it%20has%20been%20vindicated%20by%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Revenue%20Intelligence%20(DRI%E2%80%99s)%20decision%20this%20year%20to%20withdraw%20an%20appeal%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20a%20case%20against%20one%20of%20the%2040%20importers%20named%20in%202016.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20issue%20of%20overvaluation%20in%20the%20import%20of%20coal%20was%20conclusively%20settled%20by%20India%E2%80%99s%20highest%20court%20of%20law.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20asked%20if%20the%20Congress%20party%20party%20will%20initiate%20a%20probe%20against%20the%20Adani%20group%20if%20voted%20to%20power%20next%20year%2C%20Gandhi%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CWill%20definitely%20get%20it%20done%2C%20why%20not%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CLook%2C%20this%20is%20not%20about%20Adani%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20this%20Rs%2032%2C000%20crore%20has%20been%20stolen%20from%20the%20people%20of%20India%2C%20that%20is%20the%20issue%20and%20whoever%20steals%20Rs%2032%2C000%20crore%20will%20be%20investigated%2C%20why%20not%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EResponding%20to%20questions%20on%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20supremo%20Sharad%20Pawar%E2%80%99s%20recent%20meetings%20with%20Adani%2C%20Gandhi%20said%20that%20Pawar%20is%20not%20the%20prime%20minister%20of%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPawar%E2%80%99s%20NCP%20wing%20is%20a%20member%20of%20the%2026-party%20INDIA%20alliance%20which%20also%20includes%20the%20Congress.%20His%20meetings%20with%20Adani%20have%20also%20raised%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsharad-pawar-adani-group-jpc-shiv-sena-congress%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Equestions%20about%20variance%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%20opposition%20ranks%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20have%20demanded%20a%20joint%20parliamentary%20committee%20(JPC)%20probe%20against%20Adani.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSharad%20Pawar%20is%20not%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India.%20Sharad%20Pawar%20is%20not%20protecting%20Mr%20Adani%2C%20Mr%20Modi%20is%20and%20that%20is%20why%2C%20I%20ask%20Mr%20Modi%20this%20question%20and%20not%20Mr%20Sharad%20Pawar.%20If%20Mr%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C(If)%20Sharad%20Pawar%20was%20sitting%20as%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India%2C%20and%20if%20he%20was%20protecting%20Mr.%20Adani%2C%20then%20I%20would%20be%20asking%20Mr.%20Sharad%20Pawar%20that%20question.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697629813000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18164052%2FUntitled-design-2-3.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Felectricity-gautam-adani-rahul-gandhi-congress-press-conference%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress%20MP%20accused%20Adani%20of%20over-invoicing%20coal%20imports%2C%20and%20promised%20to%20probe%20the%20conglomerate%20if%20voted%20to%20power%20in%20next%20year%E2%80%99s%20general%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A89%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Felectricity-gautam-adani-rahul-gandhi-congress-press-conference%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SC%20Offers%20Protection%20to%20'Runaway'%20Married%20Couple%2C%20Directs%20Police%20to%20Counsel%20Woman's%20Family%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F02153554%2Fkhadija-yousaf-lKwp3-FQomY-unsp